  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要给webhook服务设计一个熔断器模式，核心就是三个状态：Closed、Open和HalfOpen。Closed状态是正常放行所有请求，但要监控故障率。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Closed",
        "Open",
        "HalfOpen",
        "All requests flow through",
        "Monitor failure rate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那Closed状态累积失败的话怎么触发熔断？需要设置具体的阈值吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Closed",
        "Failure Threshold Exceeded",
        "Increment failure count"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，我们定个规则：60秒内出现5次失败就触发，从Closed跳到Open状态。每次失败要increment failure count，成功的话要reset failure count。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Closed",
        "Open",
        "5 failures in 60s",
        "Increment failure count",
        "Reset failure count"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了Closed到Open的转换，以及Closed状态内部的自循环。那Open状态的行为呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Closed -- Open",
        "Closed -- Closed",
        "Failed Request",
        "Successful Request"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Open状态要完全阻断请求，fail fast，直接返回错误或者缓存响应，不要真的调用下游服务。同时要等一个30秒的冷却期，之后才能进入HalfOpen试探。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Open",
        "Fail fast, don't call service",
        "30s wait period",
        "HalfOpen",
        "Block all requests",
        "Return cached response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "HalfOpen状态是只放有限流量过去测试对吧？如果测试成功就reset circuit回到Closed，失败就back to open state？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HalfOpen",
        "Limited requests allowed",
        "Reset circuit",
        "Back to open state",
        "Test Request Successful",
        "Test Request Failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，HalfOpen要quick transition decision，监控success rate。等待测试期间也是limited throughput，不能放大流量。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HalfOpen",
        "Quick transition decision",
        "Monitor success rate",
        "Waiting for Test",
        "Limited requests allowed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "三个状态的详细注释我也补上了：Closed侧重监控和计数，Open侧重阻断和日志，HalfOpen侧重试探和快速决策。你看看整体结构？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "note right of Closed",
        "note right of Open",
